## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in educational technology. The effectiveness of each learning modality can vary significantly depending on individual learning styles, course content, and institutional support. Additionally, the rapid evolution of online learning platforms may lead to changes in their effectiveness and accessibility over time. Further research is needed to explore the long-term impacts of online learning on educational outcomes.